### Step 6 — `src/accounts.ts`

Exports `ResolvedPulseBoardAccount`, `listPulseBoardAccountIds`, `resolveDefaultPulseBoardAccountId`, `resolvePulseBoardAccount`, `listEnabledPulseBoardAccounts`.

Resolution priority for `apiKey`:
1. `PULSEBOARD_API_KEY` env var (default account only)
