```

**`api.ts`:** `export * from "./src/accounts.js"; export * from "./src/setup-surface.js";`

**`channel-config-api.ts`:** `export { PulseBoardChannelConfigSchema } from "./src/config-schema.js";`

### Step 20 — Tests

**`src/channel.test.ts`** — smoke test mirroring `irc/src/channel.test.ts`:
- Verifies `pulseBoardPlugin.outbound?.base.textChunkLimit === 4000`
- Verifies `chunker("alpha beta", 5)` → `["alpha", "beta"]`
